{
  "stem": "13096.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he had his leg amputated.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They went there that night.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "He had his leg amputated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They took him from the hospital, from there, with his leg and his blood coming out, you know, without even-- because he was in this-- in their theater.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They took him out from the theater, with the leg 1/2 there, you know, hanging, whatever.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They-- the leg was out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They took him into the boat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Funny enough, this man survive the boat to-- you know, the trip on the boat; survived the train 16 days.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he arrive in Auschwitz to be cremated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he was suffering.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was crying.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had-- nobody had any-- any medication to give to him.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Imagine an old man of 80 with the leg cut off and the blood coming out?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So when you arrived in Athens, where did you go?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They-- they took us to Haidari, which is the main prison of Athens, the Greek prison of Athens.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were there, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, the-- the old ladies, and you know, like my mothers, and all these, they thought, you know, they had premonition that something wrong was coming to us.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they start crying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They wouldn't eat.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, the first day they give us nothing to eat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the second day, they give us some soup and some stale bread, which we ate it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were very hungry.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And after three days, they took us to the rail-- you know, to the stations, and they put us in the-- into the wagons-- those famous trains, you know?",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Can I just take you back?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "How did you get to Athens from the port that you arrived at?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With buses.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "With buses.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They put us into the bus.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
